PN,39701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1784215104
OL,3,CMan jailed for trying to kidnap woman
OL,4,Cby posing as a taxi driver
OL,6,FA man who kidnapped a vulnerable woman
OL,7,Fby posing as a taxi driver has been
OL,8,Fjailed.
OL,10,FThe woman had been enjoying a night
OL,11,Fout with friends in the Groat Market
OL,12,Farea of Newcastle city centre on
OL,13,FSaturday 20 December before booking a
OL,14,Ftaxi home at around 2.20am the
OL,15,Ffollowing day.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1784215104
OL,3,CMan jailed for trying to kidnap woman
OL,4,Cby posing as a taxi driver
OL,6,FWhile looking for her driver outside,
OL,7,Fthe woman was approached by Kuldip
OL,8,FChahal, a man she did not know. He
OL,9,Fspoke to her before picking her up
OL,10,Ffrom the floor and putting his arm
OL,11,Faround her.
OL,13,FHe repeatedly directed and physically
OL,14,Fguided her through crowded streets for
OL,15,Faround ten minutes towards his car
OL,16,Fparked on Fenkle Street.
OL,18,FChahal dragged and forced her into his
OL,19,Ffront passenger seat after telling her
OL,20,Fhe was taking her home.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1784215104
OL,3,CMan jailed for trying to kidnap woman
OL,4,Cby posing as a taxi driver
OL,6,FHowever, he was unaware he was already
OL,7,Fbeing observed by police officers as
OL,8,Fpart of Operation Salus, working to
OL,9,Fidentify vulnerability in the night-
OL,10,Ftime economy. He was stopped before he
OL,11,Fcould get away.
OL,13,FChahal was arrested on suspicion of
OL,14,Fkidnap after officers found the woman
OL,15,Fdid not know him by name.
OL,17,FFootage from Northumbria Police
OL,18,Fcaptures the moment Chahal forced the
OL,19,Fwoman into his car before officers
OL,20,Fstopped him
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1784215104
OL,3,CMan jailed for trying to kidnap woman
OL,4,Cby posing as a taxi driver
OL,6,FFurther enquiries by the investigating
OL,7,Fofficer, working alongside
OL,8,Fneighbourhood policing colleagues,
OL,9,Fquickly established that Chahal was
OL,10,Fnot a licensed taxi driver and had
OL,11,Fapproached several other women in the
OL,12,Fcity centre before targeting the
OL,13,Fvictim.
OL,15,FThe now 51-year-old, of Plessey Road,
OL,16,FBlyth, was also captured on a trawl of
OL,17,FCCTV footage physically picking up the
OL,18,Fvictim from the ground, with the
OL,19,Fevidence gathered leading to him being
OL,20,Fcharged.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1784215104
OL,3,CMan jailed for trying to kidnap woman
OL,4,Cby posing as a taxi driver
OL,6,FDespite denying the offence, he was
OL,7,Ffound guilty following a one-week
OL,8,Ftrial at Newcastle Crown Court in May.
OL,10,FHe returned to the same court on
OL,11,FThursday 9 July where he was sentenced
OL,12,Fto seven years in prison.
OL,14,FHe will also serve an extended licence
OL,15,Fperiod of three years and was made
OL,16,Fsubject to a lifetime Sexual Harm
OL,17,FPrevention Order.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1784215104
OL,3,CMan jailed for trying to kidnap woman
OL,4,Cby posing as a taxi driver
OL,6,FDuring the hearing, an impact
OL,7,Fstatement was shared from the woman
OL,8,FChahal targeted, who said her
OL,9,F"confidence, independence and sense of
OL,10,Fsafety" had been significantly
OL,11,Faffected.
OL,13,FShe said: "Before this happened, I was
OL,14,Fa confident and sociable young woman
OL,15,Fwho enjoyed spending time with my
OL,16,Ffriends.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1784215104
OL,3,CMan jailed for trying to kidnap woman
OL,4,Cby posing as a taxi driver
OL,6,F"I never imagined that something so
OL,7,Ffrightening could happen to me whilst
OL,8,Fsimply spending time with friends.
OL,9,FWhat happened that night has changed
OL,10,Fme.
OL,12,F"Since that night, I have struggled to
OL,13,Ffeel safe in situations that I
OL,14,Fpreviously would not have thought
OL,15,Ftwice about.
OL,17,F"The thing I struggle with most is
OL,18,Fknowing that I was vulnerable and that
OL,19,Fsomebody chose to take advantage of
OL,20,Fthat vulnerability.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1784215104
OL,3,CMan jailed for trying to kidnap woman
OL,4,Cby posing as a taxi driver
OL,6,F"I was a young woman trying to get
OL,7,Fhome after a night out with friends.
OL,9,F"Instead, I became the target of a man
OL,10,Fmore than twice my age who saw my
OL,11,Fvulnerability and chose to exploit it.
OL,13,F"I was not seen as a person. I was
OL,14,Fseen as an opportunity. That is
OL,15,Fsomething I find incredibly difficult
OL,16,Fto come to terms with."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1784215104
OL,3,CMan jailed for trying to kidnap woman
OL,4,Cby posing as a taxi driver
OL,6,FReacting to the verdict, Detective
OL,7,FConstable Courtney Cran, who led the
OL,8,Finvestigation for Northumbria Police,
OL,9,Fsaid: "Firstly, I would like to
OL,10,Fcommend the victim-survivor, who has
OL,11,Fshown immense bravery, resilience, and
OL,12,Fcomposure throughout the full
OL,13,Finvestigation and the lengthy criminal
OL,14,Fproceedings that followed.
OL,16,F"Chahal is a predatory individual who
OL,17,Fdeliberately targeted a lone,
OL,18,Fvulnerable young woman who was simply
OL,19,Ftrying to get home safely after a
OL,20,Fnight out with friends.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1784215104
OL,3,CMan jailed for trying to kidnap woman
OL,4,Cby posing as a taxi driver
OL,6,F"He showed absolutely no regard for
OL,7,Fher welfare or the devastating impact
OL,8,Fhis actions would have, repeatedly
OL,9,Fdenying any wrongdoing and forcing her
OL,10,Fto relive her trauma during the trial.
OL,12,F"Working alongside neighbourhood
OL,13,Fpolicing colleagues and key partners,
OL,14,FI was quickly able to unravel Chahal's
OL,15,Fweb of lies and present clear evidence
OL,16,Fof his intentions that evening."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1784215104
OL,3,CMan jailed for trying to kidnap woman
OL,4,Cby posing as a taxi driver
OL,6,FShe added: "Thanks to the vigilance of
OL,7,Fofficers that evening, who saw
OL,8,Fsomething was not quite right, they
OL,9,Fwere quickly able to intervene and
OL,10,Fbring Chahal to a stop.
OL,12,F"The woman was safeguarded within
OL,13,Fminutes, after it became clear she had
OL,14,Fno idea who this man was and had been
OL,15,Ftricked and forced into his vehicle.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1784215104
OL,3,CMan jailed for trying to kidnap woman
OL,4,Cby posing as a taxi driver
OL,6,F"This has been a terrifying ordeal for
OL,7,Fher, and while incidents of this
OL,8,Fnature remain rare, this case
OL,9,Fdemonstrates exactly why proactive
OL,10,Foperations such as Operation Salus are
OL,11,Fso important. We regularly deploy
OL,12,Ftactics to identify anyone who is
OL,13,Fvulnerable, especially after a night
OL,14,Fout.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1784215104
OL,3,CMan jailed for trying to kidnap woman
OL,4,Cby posing as a taxi driver
OL,6,F"While no result will ever take away
OL,7,Fthe sheer impact of Chahal's
OL,8,Foffending, I hope today's outcome
OL,9,Fprovides the victim-survivor with some
OL,10,Fsense of justice and allows her to
OL,11,Fbegin moving forward now that he is
OL,12,Fset to spend a lengthy spell behind
OL,13,Fbars.
OL,15,F"As a force, we'll continue to take a
OL,16,Fproactive approach to keep people safe
OL,17,Fin our cities and towns, working
OL,18,Ftogether with partner agencies to
OL,19,Fcrack down on suspicious activity such
OL,20,Fas fake and unlicensed taxi drivers."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G13/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
